config ZMK_MODIFIER_NOTIFIER
    bool "Send modifier state changes over raw HID"
    depends on RAW_HID
    default n
    help
      Sends a 32-byte raw HID report whenever the explicit modifier state
      changes. The packet contains the modifier bitmask (with handedness
      preserved -- left/right ctrl/shift/alt/gui are distinct bits) so a
      host-side script can display which modifiers are currently active.
